{
  "stem": "25834.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the-- We-- I was lucky, because, this time, I have some small money, generally speaking.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was enough bribe the [LAUGHS] Soviet soldier-- and my watch. 20 zloty and my watch, and we go away, six guys.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And because was we know-- we never like Soviet, because what the Soviet promise, never keep the promise.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we divide for three parts, and we go three ways.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I took west way with my friend.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One go to the east, to Vilno, and was captured later, there, by Soviet.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And two went to-- because very close to Lithuania border-- go to Litva and later, there, to Sweden, and, from there, go to England and fight during the Cold War in English Navy against the Hitler.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's the story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I come back to Warsaw, 1939.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I'm going through the Bug.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That's big river in Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And standing up to the knee in the water.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "After it was dark, we jump, and we go through the water to Poland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because, meantime, the Soviet and German, after shake hand and kiss each other, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] put the border on the River Bug.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "What divided Poland, east and west, up to the Bug River took Soviet, and from the River Bug take the German.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And was, you know, that divide the Poland only for one year, because two-- but then later, there start fighting each other.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You know about this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And that's-- I come back to Warsaw, 1939, before Christmas.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That was December.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I saw, during this walk-- a couple hundred miles, from the east to Warsaw, I go by foot.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I must go through the places where you not see the army, German army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And that was experience.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
